node.text:
Welcome to our Crumbl summer fair week! Join Brelynn and Gabe from Crumbl HQ unbox this week's pink box, sharing their favorites, and kicking off this week's Crumbl Fair Game. 🎡💕
 
In addition to bringing fair flavored cookies, we will be hosting our own Crumbl Fair Game! Listen closely in this episode for your FIRST hint in our fair game, then stay tuned as we share a new hint each day on one of our social media platforms! 

The platform will switch daily so make sure you are paying close attention, to gather all the clues. Keep an eye out on Friday for where you should submit your final answer! The first FIVE people to put together the clues win a swag bag! Who's ready to CRUMBL?! 😉🍪

Step right up and try our ✨NEW✨ Cinnamon Fry Bread cookie! 

It’s a warm butter fry bread style cookie topped with melted butter and cinnamon honey buttercream. 🍞

FUN FACT: we put sweetened condensed milk on the dough BEFORE baking them! 🥛 That’s why this cookie is nice and crispy on the outside, and warm and gooey on the inside. 😋 

Have you tried this one yet? Leave us your review! 👇 #TasteWeekly #CrumblCookies

We are bringing the summer fair to YOU with this new lineup: July 19-24

🍬 COTTON CANDY 
A soft sugar cookie topped with a fluffy layer of blue and pink cotton candy frosting and sprinkled with cotton candy pop rocks. 

🍞 CINNAMON FRY BREAD (NEW)
A warm butter fry bread style cookie topped with melted butter and cinnamon honey buttercream.

🫐 BERRIES N’ CREAM (NEW)
A chilled mixed berry sugar cookie topped with fresh whipped cream and a fresh raspberry.

🍏 CARAMEL APPLE
A spiced apple cookie base paired perfectly with creamy caramel frosting and topped with a crumbly apple streusel.
 🍭 CHILLED SUGAR
Our classic sugar cookie base topped with a perfect pink swirl of almond-flavored frosting.

🍪 MILK CHOCOLATE CHIP
A warm cookie with milk chocolate chips.

🚨 GIVEAWAY CLOSED🚨
Like & tag three friends on this post 👇 for a chance to win a FREE party box! We will announce the winner tomorrow on our story.

#TasteWeekly #CrumblCookies #PinkBox
